narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: not really unless you need a QR
Only if they need for their major or if they are taking the class Credit D

I think it is a difficult class, and without a great instructor it can be hard to learn. If you have a passion for math it can be worth it, but there is a lot of learning that has to be done on your own.
Would only recommend if you need it for a requirement.
